{
  "stem": "1354.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And what-- we needed to go to the bathroom, there was a woman watching us all the time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We couldn't go separate to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to wait till the whole group had to go, and go in-- in groups.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's how we-- one day, we-- we get up, and the Russians-- no, when it was too close, Schindler had a speech to us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To tell you the truth, I don't-- in the beginning-- but then I recall something that I-- it was so many people, I hardly could even hear what he was saying.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- but he gave a speech, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, our people helped him to escape.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I did not see him escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, one more thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like, in Brinnlitz, there were guys working in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were guys working outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were bringing, like, wool to knit from outside from someplace.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was cold, so they were giving us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My sister-in-law met there a guy what he worked in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he gave her the wool.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were knitting for them the sweaters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was giving us extra soup, extra bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that way, we-- we survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As I remember, I was sitting up sometimes till 1:00 in the morning and knitting, yeah, together with my sister-in-law.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember that I was with my brother and my sister-in-law.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there-- when Schindler left, there was the food in the-- in the warehouses, and fabrics, and-- So a committee got-- some people got together, and they went and they divide a little for everybody, whatever it was left, and some food.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember my brother-- we got some cream of wheat-- and he made a fire outside.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
